{"original_text": "丙申正月十五#早课习楷#。\n致敬颜鲁公，端书勤礼碑。", "evtlist": [935], "uid": "1263406744", "dep": 0, "text": "丙申正月十五#早课习楷#。\n致敬颜鲁公，端书勤礼碑。", "pid": "", "tr": 12, "mid": "3945257815220417", "times": 1, "childnum": 11, "t": 1456106224, "totalChildren": 12, "dr": 11, "children": [{"evtlist": [935], "uid": "5506120877", "dep": 0, "text": "见过一幅南宫碑的书法，帅呆了！", "pid": "3945257815220417", "tr": 0, "mid": "3945260436176881", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1456106849, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "石跃峰62610"}, {"evtlist": [935], "uid": "2420703255", "dep": 0, "text": "我的浅见，司马先生的字有变化，朴拙圆润一些，体现了回归自然的趋势，看得出一个人的心态转向平和。以前刻意整齐中的准确和笔势锋利中的尖锐，需要功力，然窃以为秀的主要还是技艺而非境界。", "pid": "3945257815220417", "tr": 1, "mid": "3945260482350785", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1456106860, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [935], "uid": "2128838901", "dep": 0, "text": "字越写越好了！[good][good][good] ", "pid": "3945260482350785", "tr": 0, "mid": "3945262252648584", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1456107282, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "郭大侠之大者"}], "name": "武汉陈国恩"}, {"evtlist": [935], "uid": "1752017813", "dep": 0, "text": "换成毛笔后，腕力控制明显不足。", "pid": "3945257815220417", "tr": 0, "mid": "3945260557908176", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1456106878, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "兰陵醉客"}, {"evtlist": [935], "uid": "1735097913", "dep": 0, "text": "勤礼碑切记不要在初临阶段就写小楷", "pid": "3945257815220417", "tr": 0, "mid": "3945260630111052", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1456106895, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "李冠楠"}, {"evtlist": [935], "uid": "1193147044", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3945257815220417", "tr": 0, "mid": "3945261812889511", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1456107178, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "imyk"}, {"evtlist": [935], "uid": "5672005670", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3945257815220417", "tr": 0, "mid": "3945263267428960", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1456107525